    <entry>
      <title>Hexo添加新的文章和添加新的标签页</title>
      <link href="/2021/07/19/my-new-pos/"/>
      <url>/2021/07/19/my-new-pos/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="添加"><a href="#添加" class="headerlink" title="添加"></a>添加</h2><h3 id="添加新的文章"><a href="#添加新的文章" class="headerlink" title="添加新的文章"></a>添加新的文章</h3><p>在source/_post中新建md类型的文档，也可以命令行创建</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &quot;post name&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后执行<code>hexo g</code>的时候会被渲染，开头需要一些yml信息\</p><p>再执行<code>hexo d</code>就可以将其部署到github上。</p><h3 id="添加”分类”页面"><a href="#添加”分类”页面" class="headerlink" title="添加”分类”页面"></a>添加”分类”页面</h3><p>新建一个分类页面</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改source/categories/index.md</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2021-07-19 22:54:58</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2021-07-19 22:54:58</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot; (添加这行 空格需要注意)</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>themes\cactus下的_config.yml中的nav进行匹配</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nav:</span><br><span class="line">  home: /</span><br><span class="line">  about: /about/</span><br><span class="line">  articles: /archives/</span><br><span class="line">  projects: projects_url</span><br><span class="line">  categories: /categories（添加此行即可）        </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>给文章添加categories属性</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Hexo添加新的文章和添加新的标签页</span><br><span class="line">date: 2021-07-19 10:30:24</span><br><span class="line">categories: Exercise</span><br><span class="line">tags: first try</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一开始添加后，发现标签名是英文<br>后来发现是themes/cactus/languages/zh-CN.yml没做好映射</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nav:</span><br><span class="line">  home: 首页</span><br><span class="line">  about: 关于</span><br><span class="line">  articles: 归档</span><br><span class="line">  projects: 项目</span><br><span class="line">  tag: 标签</span><br><span class="line">  category: 分类</span><br><span class="line">  search: 搜索</span><br><span class="line">  categories: 分类（添加）</span><br><span class="line">  tags: 标签 (添加)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当然开始时添加标签页改为，无复数形式也是可以的</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page category</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="添加”标签”页面"><a href="#添加”标签”页面" class="headerlink" title="添加”标签”页面"></a>添加”标签”页面</h3><p>与添加分类页面几乎完全相同</p><h3 id="参考链接"><a href="#参考链接" class="headerlink" title="参考链接"></a>参考链接</h3><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/ebbbc8edcc24">Git个人博客hexo设置关于、标签、分类、归档、时间线</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/e17711e44e00">Hexo使用攻略-添加分类及标签</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Exercise </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
